From: Bryan Larsen <bryan@larsen.st>

To make the filter look right, create a file `app/assets/stylesheets/front/agility-custom-styles.css`

SHOW_PATCH
---
 .../stylesheets/front/agility-custom-styles.css    |    3 +++
 1 files changed, 3 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 app/assets/stylesheets/front/agility-custom-styles.css

diff --git a/app/assets/stylesheets/front/agility-custom-styles.css b/app/assets/stylesheets/front/agility-custom-styles.css
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..ab6dd83
--- /dev/null
+++ b/app/assets/stylesheets/front/agility-custom-styles.css
@@ -0,0 +1,3 @@
+.show-page.project .filter {float: left;}
+.show-page.project .filter form, .show-page.project .filter form div {display: inline;}
